name: KpopFanclubTrivia
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: korean pop fan trivia
des: Kpop is on the rise, and you must not want to be left behind! Test your kpop knowledge with 80+ idols and their fanclub names! Alexa will give you the name of an idol group, and you just have to say their fanclub name! Note: some groups (i.e. ReVeLulv, AROHA) are excluded because Alexa will not understand what is being said.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
